# Stripe Payment Links — wiring template
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your actual Stripe Payment Link URLs.
# Do NOT commit .env.local to git (it is already gitignored).
#
# How to create Payment Links:
# 1. Log in to https://dashboard.stripe.com
# 2. Go to Payment Links → + Create
# 3. Set price: $1,000.00 for Office Hours, $12,000.00 for Architecture Review
# 4. Set product name to match the tier (e.g. "WhiteMagic Labs — Office Hours")
# 5. Copy the Payment Link URL and paste below
# 6. Redeploy the site (the env vars are baked at build time for Next.js static export)
#
# Optional: add ?prefilled_email= to the URL if you want Stripe to collect email
# at checkout and pre-fill the booking form.

NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_OFFICE_HOURS_URL=https://buy.stripe.com/...
NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_ARCHITECTURE_REVIEW_URL=https://buy.stripe.com/...
